[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Considering thread properties**\n\nI’m thinking through the implications of setting a property to false while using a virtual factory. It seems it would remain VIRTUAL, but maybe it's better not to restore the property to keep things consistent. If the current ThreadType is set to VIRTUAL globally, then restoring the property to false or absent might still not change that ThreadType to anything other than VIRTUAL. It’s a bit of a tangled situation!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_06ab2f88d00fcbb30169fcbebb5ce4819e8b043ae6dbf77f0f\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp_L7KzOZTp7UYN9Ywz3Jk1N-E28EZYdNZhooHnA7AR-MlWb9yXgBgZGoCLI5ZqtbRGWnmlis0qDtb5Jr0Z4pswuovh8ruD8nSdKHWhQKvMIslZA20DK-xzU1nxqc74-U96OVpI1ehaWquY3dixGEjuOUz9acFRW5hbU4oxLj-SsCY7xkoBgxgfVG-bARNZSBy5tJsepOQr93oPPvy2mz1aDBX3xMjN8H8WN7r-ui_mL0MllOHU-mW90rvw5OVI2KklPKeTpCb9UB08ZGTpM5UBc34dkzY__a9pxfrjZmKtVQbKfmEjITyr9PrbsAKuHA4igJMeqe6C-8lzuLdHX6blVmNkEWJXntHdfsP8DdSH-UWhQjniNk-x1sLCXqKzb8tsp1qwZiuzp5-wUN9xexs5ExLfF2vheIIZa2zwz1kW7WQM6wsY4tNAP30X3Lc1dKcZau_iUyZp-7FeXjAMZpb0FsDBBbDdJs7uip3Ec3E1CtobbVHjzYz0mGNKDaHEmmy4e9Gtn1Puz7xPI9j5AxYEgtqz6g0EEeESIi00ceX2hpBEy639jc-IBj6ikbCksGAvVxwiijaJxPm-nklx0BbdxrlHbkxjr7HAa7iafNh_vkvkVXhrfpTQQtCCOeHIHPLEzxRlba8GLvtmgFmUOxez6kZjkuqE3qW6LoM4mpyw99tC0UE8or5cFdqGTtYE7PDKDkb2OpuD237cjmA3xE060sYgl-zEUs_rz2QP3W90O8n5C41z5WCQwJApSVbmm6P6_oz_d9GKzSGU9uPWYklnkqIFya9NqSiDVr64jxC6yGkXqx3mn9yWnWWrBaaRV9FLVE4bor5ecnc1QtsVAO8JA2exe3AjRxVaqh1KoW2hULldJb28bSayiCamkRD7WHRBOGPHL1xJETYZfiaQAotxN_fuKVG1TEc8lgXY1nuzzDnzHpz1z87SOLcTByCLz_qaMJYRMmGrcLZXIiRhJv8q8RVKWImtMBBV-Y9DD8IlZEanIaoT3BDdfEV_l4zvlaAGntFM5vRfSnH6G0GgN5t9RScpB26Q3kkwuaSwOyHKoN0z9wbnA0nA7lv8IK6klJZb2CIYG0G6MOADMC_68jbV-I3uIpct9ti_QUtJnhaNWJ2XkXrWXHVjEsL4dWxJu0xLbUO78hlQtSFZeLIJ-qs_TVVg0krwEDqM0ZDpxSXzDeOaXP06gH_P33fVMFUpy-_cedodBa383JF7MERrtw9kNtcssVvGY5YU01Ad5P8VGEIRPWS47JLBy8DPmmtZ5M54nyu1G1-pr6vi